references: Amending: Ord 4635, Ord 52110, Ord 57132. Repealing: Ord 6865, Ord 33563.
summary: An ordinance prescribing a system for numbering buildings and premises in the City of Seattle, amending Ordinance No. 4635 by adding Sections 1-a, 1-b and 1-c thereto, and repealing Ordinances Nos. 6865, 33563, Section 2 of Ordinance No. 52110 and Sections 3 and 4 of Ordinance No. 57132.
